Style FvwmTestBar* !Title, BorderWidth 3, HandleWidth 3, Sticky, CirculateSkip, WindowListSkip, NeverFocus, StaysOnBottom, !Iconifiable

DestroyModuleConfig FvwmTestBar:*
*FvwmTestBar: Geometry 200x200+2+250
*FvwmTestBar: Colorset 0
*FvwmTestBar: Rows 1
*FvwmTestBar: Columns 1
*FvwmTestBar: Frame 1
*FvwmTestBar: Font "Shadow=0 0 SE:xft:Fira Sans:Regular:size=10:antialias=True:hintstyle=slight"
#*FvwmTestBar: (1x1, Id desk0, Title "1", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 0, Colorset 11, ActiveColorset 12, Frame 1)
#*FvwmTestBar: (1x1, Id desk1, Title "2", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 1, ActiveColorset 12, Frame 1)
#*FvwmTestBar: (1x1, Id desk2, Title "3", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 2, ActiveColorset 12, Frame 1)
#*FvwmTestBar: (1x1, Id desk3, Title "4", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 3, ActiveColorset 12, Frame 1)
*FvwmTestBar: (1x1, Swallow FvwmPager 'Module FvwmPager *', Frame 1)

# FvwmButtons - FvwmPagerPanel
#
# FvwmButtons is a powerful module that can be used to build custom
# panels and docks. This config uses FvwmButtons to build the FvwmPagerPanel.
# The panel contains buttons to switch desks, FvwmPager, a system tray,
# FvwmIconMan (list of running windows), and a clock.
#
# Note - To use the system tray you must have "stalonetray" installed.
DestroyModuleConfig FvwmPagerPanel:*
*FvwmPagerPanel: Geometry 170x128+2+2
*FvwmPagerPanel: Colorset 10
*FvwmPagerPanel: Rows 180
*FvwmPagerPanel: Columns 100
*FvwmPagerPanel: Frame 0
*FvwmPagerPanel: Font "xft:Fira Sans:regular:size=10:antialias=True"
# *FvwmPagerPanel: (120x45, Icon "fvwm-logo-small.png", Frame 0)
*FvwmPagerPanel: (25x20, Id desk0, Title "0", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 1, Colorset 11, ActiveColorset 12, Frame 1)
*FvwmPagerPanel: (25x20, Id desk1, Title "1", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 2, ActiveColorset 12, Frame 1)
*FvwmPagerPanel: (25x20, Id desk2, Title "2", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 3, ActiveColorset 12, Frame 1)
*FvwmPagerPanel: (25x20, Id desk3, Title "3", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 4, ActiveColorset 12, Frame 1)
#*FvwmPagerPanel: (5x80, Frame 0)
*FvwmPagerPanel: (100x80, Swallow FvwmPager 'Module FvwmPager *', Frame 1)
#*FvwmPagerPanel: (5x80, Frame 0)